[sighs]

03:00.939 --> 03:02.355
This is my friend Vivian.

03:02.438 --> 03:04.563
She wasn't healthy enough
to make the trip.

03:04.647 --> 03:05.855
She wanted to see the ocean.

03:05.939 --> 03:06.855
Hello, Vivian.

03:06.939 --> 03:08.438
Welcome to Los Angeles.

03:08.522 --> 03:09.480
Whoa.

03:09.563 --> 03:10.772
Whoa.

03:10.855 --> 03:12.772
Whoa.

03:12.855 --> 03:13.730
[Vivian laughs]

03:13.814 --> 03:17.355
